  "title": "Contract Driver",
  "description": "<ol><li><strong>Duties Contract Driver </strong></li></ol><ul><li>Transport workers/students to and from various locations.</li><li>Adhere to allocated driving schedule and timing.</li><li>Perform any other bus driving and related duties that may be assigned from time to time.</li><li>Operate the vehicle safely and efficiently to transport passengers to various destinations as assigned by the Operations Team</li><li>Responsible for maintenance and cleanliness of the vehicle: Perform vehicle inspection before and after each trip to ensure that the vehicle is in good working condition</li><li>Must be able to use WhatsApp for communication.</li></ul><p><strong>Attractive Salary and Benefits</strong></p><p>• Basic Salary + Ad Hoc Trip earnings <br />• Insurance coverage<br />• Petrol/diesel, Cashcard and Season parking covered</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>• Valid Singapore Class 3 Driving License<br />• Valid BDVL Vocational License<br />• Monday to Saturday</p><ul><li>Only Singaporeans or PRs may apply</li><li>No agencies please</li><li>Please send your resume to safatransportsg@gmail.com ( Kindly refrain from calling. Any calls will not be entertained. )</li></ul>",
